---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Vibe AI Infrastructure"
  description="Learn AGI infrastructure through Vibe learning with Vibe Nano and Vibe Insights."
>
  <main class="landing reveal">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Learn AGI Infrastructure via Vibe Learning</p>
      <h1>Vibe AI Infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="hero-copy">
        Vibe AI Infra is a learning-first infrastructure program for the AGI era. We combine
        hands-on system building in <strong>Vibe Nano</strong> with transparent analysis in
        <strong> Vibe Insights</strong>, so every concept links to concrete engineering work.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="vision-strip">
      <p>
        Vision: make AGI infrastructure understandable, reproducible, and composable across
        silicon, software, and operations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="focus-grid">
      <a href="/nano-infra" class="focus-card nano">
        <span class="badge">Build</span>
        <h2>Vibe Nano</h2>
        <p>
          Navigate the project map, open each project page, and learn why each layer matters for AGI
          infrastructure.
        </p>
        <span class="jump">Explore Projects</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/insights" class="focus-card insights">
        <span class="badge">Analyze</span>
        <h2>Vibe Insights</h2>
        <p>
          Study performance and cost models with practical assumptions and implementation-oriented
          next steps.
        </p>
        <span class="jump">Read Insights</span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .landing {
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 20px 98px;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #1e40af;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 5.3rem);
    max-width: 15ch;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  .vision-strip {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    max-width: 930px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
    background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(219, 234, 254, 0.75), rgba(224, 242, 254, 0.68));
  }

  .vision-strip p {
    color: #1e3a8a;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .focus-grid {
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .focus-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 260px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 22px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(246, 250, 255, 0.9));
    transition: transform 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
  }

  .focus-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.26rem 0.58rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .nano .badge {
    background: #dbeafe;
    color: #1e40af;
  }

  .insights .badge {
    background: #e0f2fe;
    color: #075985;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .focus-card p {
    margin-top: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .jump {
    margin-top: auto;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding-top: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .focus-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .focus-card {
      min-height: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
